title: Model-based provider routing
---
Parse model name prefixes (e.g. 'anthropic/claude-opus-4-6') to route to the correct provider instead of always using the first. Nullclaw does case-insensitive matching with date-suffix stripping and aliases. Changes in agent.ml + provider.ml.